    "Add onions and garlic, sauté for about 2 minutes until translucent.",
    "Add bell peppers and green olives. Cook for another 5-7 minutes until vegetables are tender.",
    "Stir in lemon juice, red pepper flakes, salt to taste. Mix well.",
    "Garnish with fresh parsley before serving.",
